title: ARE YOU BLIND TO NEW LEVELS?: Why Choosing The Hardest Possible Path Is a Good Idea, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO310
itunes:title: ARE YOU BLIND TO NEW LEVELS?: Why Choosing The Hardest Possible Path Is a Good Idea, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO310
description: Everybody wants to be happy. Everybody wants to be successful. So why isn't everyone happy & successful? The truth is, it's not because people aren't willing to work hard. A ton of people in the world work hard & are still not happy & successful. The problem is in how they approach the work. In this episode, I talk about why choosing the hardest path possible is a good idea & the incredible thing that happens when you push yourself beyond your limits.
